After much trial &amp; error, I am pleased to report I found the answer!  Eureka!

It was one simple change on one line in the CSS:

this...
```
    .navbar-nav li:hover &gt; .dropdown-menu {
        display: block;
    }
```
to...
```
    .navbar-nav li:hover &gt; .dropdown-menu {
        display:grid;  /* changing &quot;block&quot; to &quot;grid&quot; got everything working (except for IE11, but I&#39;ll report that elsewhere)
    }
```

